
Go to the market
Buy fresh or dry fish, palm oil(red),pepper, magi,and salt.
Get corn meal flower
Start by boiling the fish when ready put oil,magi,pepper.
Allow it to steam for a while and make sure it taste.
To cook fufu corn,boil water and put the corn flower while stirring.
Mix for a while and add water.
Allow it to steam and continue the mixing.
When ready serve with the tim tim
